                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4249" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1047</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8498 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">固本守正、以变应变：日春茶业的战略突围</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Keep business philosophy, Timely change: RiChun’s strategic change</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘闲月，万文海，陈建春，刘彩霞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华侨大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">日春茶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">21 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多元化；后向一体化；日春茶业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">diversification strategy; backward integration strategy; RiChun Tea Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了日春茶业从县市级区域品牌到业务覆盖19个省，拥有310多家全国直营店的成长历程。此过程中，日春茶业根据市场和竞争变动情况，发挥核心资源和能力的协同优势，战略上主动求变、应变，经历了从单一业务起步向“多品类、多品牌”的成功转型；从终端连锁销售为主向全产业链型企业演变，绘出了独具优势的共同经营主线，成为国内亿元以上规模茶企中唯一一家坚持100%直营连锁专卖的公司。持续的动态演变过程中，日春始终坚持“产销中国好茶”的愿景和“真品质，不二价”的经营理念不动摇，通过自建的“三标”体系严格控制原材料质量、产品价格和服务标准。以变应变中坚持固本守正，一动一静的协同演变获取了持续的竞争优势。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the growth of the RiChun Tea Company from the county-level regional brand to the business coverage of 19 provinces, with more than 310 national direct-operated stores. In the process, according to the market and competition changes, Richun Tea Company has taken advantage of the synergy of core resources and capabilities, strategically seeking change and response, and experienced a successful transition from a single business to “multi-category, multi-brand”; the RiChun Tea Company has evolved from terminal chain sales to full-industry chain-type enterprises, and has drawn a unique joint business line., it has become the only company in China that has 100% direct sales in the scale of tea enterprises above 100 million yuan. In the continuous dynamic evolution process, Richun always adheres to the vision of “production and sales of good Chinese tea” and the business philosophy of “true quality, one-price”. The self-built “three standard” system strictly controls the quality of raw materials, product prices, and service standards. In the process of adapting to change, it has achieved a sustainable competitive advantage by adhering to the principle of solidarity and stability.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司层战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-11</td>
                            </tr>
